Overview

This package provides support for Standard Data Types:

enumerated>/dt>
support for an enumerated structure, which is a structure that contains fields index, choice, and choices.
timeStamp
Support fgor a structure that holds a timeStamp
alarm
Support for a structure that contains data representing an alarm
